# CRUD Inertia Shadcn - CRUD Module

Guide to generate complete CRUD modules with **necro304/crud-inertia-shadcn**:
- **Backend**: Laravel 12, Spatie Query Builder, Auditing, Soft Deletes
- **Frontend**: Vue 3, TypeScript, Inertia.js v2, Shadcn-vue, TanStack Table

## Generate CRUD

```bash
php artisan make:crud Product name:string description:text price:decimal:nullable stock:integer
```

**Generates**:
- Model (SoftDeletes, Auditable)
- Controller (QueryBuilder, Inertia)
- Form Requests (Store/Update)
- API Resource
- Vue pages (Index, Create, Edit, Show)
- Form Component (Shadcn UI)
- Migration

### Command Options

```bash
php artisan make:crud Post --no-soft-deletes  # Without soft deletes
php artisan make:crud Comment --no-auditing   # Without auditing
php artisan make:crud Tag --no-views          # Backend only
php artisan make:crud UserProfile --table=profiles  # Custom table name
php artisan make:crud Product --force         # Overwrite existing files
```

### Field Syntax

```bash
name:string
email:string:unique
price:decimal:nullable
is_active:boolean
published_at:timestamp:nullable
```

